sentences: Sas Metcalfe is President, Global Creative, of Kobalt Music and has been at the company since it was founded in 2001.
Metcalfe was honoured in Billboard's Women In Music awards in 2015 and 2016.
In 1986, she became an A&R Manager at Arista Records, a position she held for three years.
